                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "frequency": "once per day, plus overcharge",
                    "effect": "You cast  *false vitality* of the indicated rank. During the duration of the spell, wisps that resemble spirits flit around you as long as you have any temporary Hit Points from  *false vitality* , and you can use the following action.",
